{"tid":2197562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"花木蘭　木蘭原來是譯名　漢字亦可譯做慕容","createTime":"2020-09-10T16:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T16:50:29.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b7352c79cd4228f4d4b15d4e94b1caaf3aac26d8","tid":2197562,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=773456753197980&amp;set=a.113816715828657&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D773456753197980%26set%3Da.113816715828657%26type%3D3&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=9a0c89ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=773456753197980&amp;set=a.113816715828657&amp;type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8OM89bq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8OM89bq.jpg&h=ed20275d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Yik Lim<br />\n<br />\n木蘭兩個漢字讓人聯想到花木芝蘭之屬，但其實它是氏族名、而非單一人名。有考證木蘭於古鮮卑語中，或有打獵之義，或有河流之義；而現代蒙古語中的Мөрөн就是河流之義，亦可拼寫為M&ouml;r&ouml;n/Murun。今日蒙古共和國有座城市即名為M&ouml;r&ouml;n(木倫市)，意思即從河流來。<br />\n<br />\nМөрөн/Murun/M&ouml;r&ouml;n還有另一個典故：它是古代中亞內亞赫赫有名的鮮卑貴族家門之名，或拼寫為Muren，有時也被拼寫為Murong。<br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得自己跟它們不太認識，但其實你一定聽過他們，在古代漢字記載文獻中，他們被這樣書寫下來：<br />\n<br />\n慕容氏"},{"pid":"2a1dad7b25203bd141b2c2e95a4f7bf69757b964","tid":2197562,"uid":313162,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"慕容公子啲fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}